            "id": 6422305,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指上漲290.41點至14788.8659點，漲幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間16日02:31，深證成指上漲290.41點（或2%），暫報14788.87點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+3.25%</li><li>近 1 月：+1.52%</li><li>近 3 月：+1.34%</li><li>近 6 月：+10.52%</li><li>今年以來：+7.2%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>青蒿素概念領漲+3.73%。其中    德龍匯能(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000593:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000593\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000593-CN</a>)            上漲        10.02%            ;        新和成(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002001:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002001\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002001-CN</a>)            上漲        3.44%            ;        潤都股份(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002923:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002923\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002923-CN</a>)            下跌        2.52%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>稀缺資源概念領漲+3.55%。其中    翔鷺鎢業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002842:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002842\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002842-CN</a>)            上漲        8.4%            ;        恆邦股份(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002237:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002237\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002237-CN</a>)            上漲        8.26%            ;        西藏礦業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000762:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000762\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000762-CN</a>)            上漲        7.17%    。</p></section></main>",
